</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-59_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Here's a detailed look at each course available for volunteers in health and social care settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-61_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-62_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-63_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-64_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-65_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-66_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Prostock-studio Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-68_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-69_ pf-heading-1-h3">Health and safety for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-71_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers will learn about health and safety legislation, hazard identification, risk assessment processes, and emergency response protocols - essential knowledge for maintaining a safe working environment.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-73_ pf-heading-1-h3">Fire safety for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-75_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course covers the fundamentals of fire safety, including the causes of fire, fire prevention, how to use fire-fighting equipment, and evacuation procedures to ensure volunteers can respond effectively in emergencies.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-77_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conflict resolution for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-79_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Participants are trained to manage and resolve conflicts peacefully. This course focuses on understanding the sources of conflict and learning negotiation and de-escalation techniques crucial in volunteer settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-81_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-82_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-83_ pf-heading-1-h3">Infection prevention and control for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-85_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">A vital course that teaches volunteers the principles of infection control, methods to prevent the spread of infections and best practices for hygiene - critical in today’s health - conscious environments.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-87_ pf-heading-1-h3">Moving and assisting for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-89_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course provides essential training on safe moving and handling techniques to prevent injuries and ensure the safety of volunteers and those they assist.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-91_ pf-heading-1-h3">Safeguarding adults for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-93_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers learn about the legal and practical aspects of safeguarding adults, including recognising signs of abuse, understanding legal safeguards, and responding appropriately to safeguarding concerns.
