</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-143_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course offers foundational adult first aid training, teaching volunteers to manage common medical emergencies until professional help arrives.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-145_ pf-heading-1-h3">First aid awareness (Paediatric) - Level 2
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-147_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course is specifically designed for those who work with children and covers essential first-aid techniques needed to address and manage paediatric emergencies effectively.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-149_ pf-heading-1-h3">Designated safeguarding lead - Level 3
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-151_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This is a more advanced course for volunteers who become safeguarding leads within their organisations. It includes comprehensive training on all aspects of safeguarding, coordinating with authorities, and leading a safeguarding team.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-153_ pf-heading-1-h3">Training courses for trustees
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-155_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Trustees can benefit from tailored courses covering governance, compliance, and leadership skills. These courses help them fulfil their roles effectively and ensure the integrity of their organisations.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-157_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-158_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-159_ pf-heading-1-h3">Why are these volunteer courses important?
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-161_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Our training ensures that volunteers are well-prepared and confident in their roles and that the organisations they represent comply with the Charity Commission, the Care Quality Commission (CQC), and other regulatory bodies like Ofsted and the Health and Safety Executive (HSE). By equipping volunteers with these essential skills, we help create safer, more efficient, and more compliant environments that enhance the quality of care provided and the overall effectiveness of charitable operations.
</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-163_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w" width="1175" height="797" alt="Volunteer essentials: statutory and mandatory training requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Volunteer essentials: statutory and mandatory training requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-164_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-165_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages&nbsp;via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-167_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-168_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130454" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130454 1536w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Meeting legal obligations: statutory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Meeting legal obligations: statutory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-169_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtR