</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-182_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Here's a detailed look at each course available for volunteers in health and social care settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-184_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-185_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-186_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-187_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.png?v=1714130281 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-188_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-189_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Prostock-studio Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-191_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-192_ pf-heading-1-h3">Health and safety for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-194_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers will learn about health and safety legislation, hazard identification, risk assessment processes, and emergency response protocols - essential knowledge for maintaining a safe working environment.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-196_ pf-heading-1-h3">Fire safety for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-198_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course covers the fundamentals of fire safety, including the causes of fire, fire prevention, how to use fire-fighting equipment, and evacuation procedures to ensure volunteers can respond effectively in emergencies.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-200_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conflict resolution for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-202_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Participants are trained to manage and resolve conflicts peacefully. This course focuses on understanding the sources of conflict and learning negotiation and de-escalation techniques crucial in volunteer settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-204_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-205_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-206_ pf-heading-1-h3">Infection prevention and control for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-208_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">A vital course that teaches volunteers the principles of infection control, methods to prevent the spread of infections and best practices for hygiene - critical in today’s health - conscious environments.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-210_ pf-heading-1-h3">Moving and assisting for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-212_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course provides essential training on safe moving and handling techniques to prevent injuries and ensure the safety of volunteers and those they assist.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-214_ pf-heading-1-h3">Safeguarding adults for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-216_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers learn about the legal and practical aspects of safeguarding adults, including recognising signs of abuse, understanding legal safeguards, and responding appropriately to safeguarding concerns.
</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-218_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6.png?v=1714139093" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6.png?v=1714139093 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_1500x.png?v=1714139093 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_1000x.png?v=1714139093 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_500x.png?v=1714139093 320w" width="1542" height="1028" alt="Ensuring compliance mandatory training for volunteer organisations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -.png__PID:4195704c-5780-4f68-a350-720d9222acd4" title="Ensuring compliance: mandatory training for volunteer organisations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-219_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-220_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by nenetus via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-222_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><d