 via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-227_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-228_ pf-heading-1-h3">Equality, diversity and human rights for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-230_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course ensures volunteers understand and promote equality, embrace diversity, and uphold human rights within their roles, creating an inclusive environment for all service users.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-232_ pf-heading-1-h3">Preventing radicalisation for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-234_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Teaches volunteers about the risks associated with radicalisation and provides them with the skills to identify signs of radicalisation and understand the steps to help prevent it.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-236_ pf-heading-1-h3">Data security awareness for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-238_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course is crucial for volunteers handling sensitive information in this digital age. It covers data protection principles and secure data handling practices to comply with legal standards like GDPR.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-240_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-241_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-242_ pf-heading-1-h3">Safeguarding children for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-244_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Similar to safeguarding adults, this course focuses on protecting children. Volunteers learn about the types of abuse, signs of abuse in children, and appropriate measures to take if child abuse is suspected.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-246_ pf-heading-1-h3">Emergency first aid at work (EFAW) - Level 3
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-248_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">It is an intensive course that equips volunteers with the skills to handle emergencies, provide first aid, and potentially save lives in critical moments.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-250_ pf-heading-1-h3">Basic life support (Adult resuscitation) - Level 2
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-252_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers are trained in basic life support techniques for adults, including CPR, essential skills in emergencies where medical response might be delayed.
</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-254_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.png?v=1714130281 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Compliance made simple: mandatory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Compliance made simple: mandatory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-255_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-256_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by seventyfourimages via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-258_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-259_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1440" height="960" alt="Keeping volunteers safe: mandatory training guidelines - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Keeping volunteers safe: mandatory training guidelines - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-260_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-261_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-263_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-264_ pf-heading-1-h3">First aid awareness (Adult) - Level 2
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-266_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course offers foundational adult first aid training, teaching volunteers to manage common medical emergencies until professional help arrives.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-268_ pf-heading-1-h3">First aid awareness (Paediatric) - Level 2
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-270_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course is specifically designed for those who work with children and covers essential first-aid techniques needed to address and manage paediatric emergencies effectively.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-272_ pf-heading-1-h3">Designated safeguarding lead - Level 3
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-274_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This is a more advanced course for volunteers who become safeguarding leads within their organisations. It includes comprehensive training on all aspects of safeguarding, coordinating with authorities, and leading a safeguarding team.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-276_ pf-heading-1-h3">Training courses for trustees
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-278_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Trustees can benefit from tailored courses covering governance, compliance, and leadership skills. These courses help them fulfil their roles effectively and ensure the integrity of their organisations.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-280_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-281_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-282_ pf-heading-1-h3">Why are these volunteer courses important?
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-284_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Our training ensures that volunteers are well-prepared and confident in their roles and that the organisations they represent comply with the Charity Commission, the Care Quality Commission (CQC), and other regulatory bodies like Ofsted and the Health and Safety Executive (HSE). By equipping volunteers with these essential skills, we help create safer, more efficient, and more compliant environments that enhance the quality of care provided and the overall effectiveness of charitable operations.
</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-286_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Volunteer_essentials_statutory_and_mandatory_training_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1175" height="797" alt="Volunteer essentials: statutory and mandatory training requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Volunteer essentials: statutory and mandatory training requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-287_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-288_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by YuriArcursPeopleimages&nbsp;via Envato Elements</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-290_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-291_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130454" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130454 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.png?v=1714130454 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130454 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Meeting_legal_obligations_statutory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130454 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Meeting legal obligations: statutory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Meeting legal obligations: statutory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-292_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-293_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Pressmaster via Envato Elements</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:6;--c-md:6;--c-lg:6"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-295_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-296_ pf-heading-1-h3">Join our volunteer mandatory training programs
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-298_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">We invite organisations and individual volunteers to explore these courses and choose those that best meet their needs. We are committed to providing the highest-quality training to help volunteers and organisations achieve their full potential, ensure compliance, enhance safety, and promote excellence across the board.
