</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-d1e7" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-djVWQC gRHrFs pf-300_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-ggqHwD fxhwFP"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-301_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-302_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-303_ pf-heading-1-h3">Volunteer mandatory and statutory training courses
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-305_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Here's a detailed look at each course available for volunteers in health and social care settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-307_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-308_"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-309_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-310_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-311_ pf-heading-1-h3">Health and safety for volunteers
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.png?v=1714130281 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Essential_training_for_volunteers_statutory_and_mandatory_requirements_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Essential training for volunteers: statutory and mandatory requirements - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-313_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-314_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by Prostock-studio Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-316_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers will learn about health and safety legislation, hazard identification, risk assessment processes, and emergency response protocols - essential knowledge for maintaining a safe working environment.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-318_ pf-heading-1-h3">Fire safety for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-320_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course covers the fundamentals of fire safety, including the causes of fire, fire prevention, how to use fire-fighting equipment, and evacuation procedures to ensure volunteers can respond effectively in emergencies.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-322_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conflict resolution for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-324_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Participants are trained to manage and resolve conflicts peacefully. This course focuses on understanding the sources of conflict and learning negotiation and de-escalation techniques crucial in volunteer settings.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-326_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-327_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-328_ pf-heading-1-h3">Infection prevention and control for volunteers
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6.png?v=1714139093" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6.png?v=1714139093 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_1500x.png?v=1714139093 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_1000x.png?v=1714139093 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ensuring_compliance_mandatory_training_for_volunteer_organisations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_17ed017c-2bd7-48b3-bccc-b7c3acb94ad6_500x.png?v=1714139093 320w" width="1542" height="1028" alt="Ensuring compliance mandatory training for volunteer organisations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -.png__PID:4195704c-5780-4f68-a350-720d9222acd4" title="Ensuring compliance: mandatory training for volunteer organisations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-330_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-331_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by nenetus via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-333_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">A vital course that teaches volunteers the principles of infection control, methods to prevent the spread of infections and best practices for hygiene - critical in today’s health - conscious environments.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-335_ pf-heading-1-h3">Moving and assisting for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-337_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course provides essential training on safe moving and handling techniques to prevent injuries and ensure the safety of volunteers and those they assist.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-339_ pf-heading-1-h3">Safeguarding adults for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-341_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers learn about the legal and practical aspects of safeguarding adults, including recognising signs of abuse, understanding legal safeguards, and responding appropriately to safeguarding concerns.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-343_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-344_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-345_ pf-heading-1-h3">Equality, diversity and human rights for volunteers
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_volunteers_understanding_statutory_training_obligations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_volunteers_understanding_statutory_training_obligations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_volunteers_understanding_statutory_training_obligations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Empowering_volunteers_understanding_statutory_training_obligations_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1440" height="920" alt="Empowering volunteers: understanding statutory training obligations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Empowering volunteers: understanding statutory training obligations - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-347_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-348_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by vanenunes

 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-350_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course ensures volunteers understand and promote equality, embrace diversity, and uphold human rights within their roles, creating an inclusive environment for all service users.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-352_ pf-heading-1-h3">Preventing radicalisation for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-354_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Teaches volunteers about the risks associated with radicalisation and provides them with the skills to identify signs of radicalisation and understand the steps to help prevent it.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-356_ pf-heading-1-h3">Data security awareness for volunteers
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-358_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course is crucial for volunteers handling sensitive information in this digital age. It covers data protection principles and secure data handling practices to comply with legal standards like GDPR.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-360_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-361_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-362_ pf-heading-1-h3">Safeguarding children for volunteers
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1500x.png?v=1714130281 1280w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Compliance_made_simple_mandatory_training_for_volunteers_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1613" height="1075" alt="Compliance made simple: mandatory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Compliance made simple: mandatory training for volunteers - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-364_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-365_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by seventyfourimages via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-367_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Similar to safeguarding adults, this course focuses on protecting children. Volunteers learn about the types of abuse, signs of abuse in children, and appropriate measures to take if child abuse is suspected.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-369_ pf-heading-1-h3">Emergency first aid at work (EFAW) - Level 3
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-371_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">It is an intensive course that equips volunteers with the skills to handle emergencies, provide first aid, and potentially save lives in critical moments.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-373_ pf-heading-1-h3">Basic life support (Adult resuscitation) - Level 2</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-375_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Volunteers are trained in basic life support techniques for adults, including CPR, essential skills in emergencies where medical response might be delayed.
</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-377_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-djTQOc gLxCly pf-378_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-379_ pf-heading-1-h3">First aid awareness (Adult) - Level 2
</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.png?v=1714130281 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_1000x.png?v=1714130281 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Keeping_volunteers_safe_mandatory_training_guidelines_-_ComplyPlus_LMS_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_500x.png?v=1714130281 320w" width="1440" height="960" alt="Keeping volunteers safe: mandatory training guidelines - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Keeping volunteers safe: mandatory training guidelines - ComplyPlus LMS™ - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gplwNw cwEcYX pf-381_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-382_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-384_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course offers foundational adult first aid training, teaching volunteers to manage common medical emergencies until professional help arrives.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-386_ pf-heading-1-h3">First aid awareness (Paediatric) - Level 2
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-388_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This course is specifically designed for those who work with children and covers essential first-aid techniques needed to address and manage paediatric emergencies effectively.</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-390_ pf-heading-1-h3">Designated safeguarding lead - Level 3
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-392_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">This is a more advanced course for volunteers who become safeguarding leads within their organisations. It includes comprehensive training on all aspects of safeguarding, coordinating with authorities, and leading a safeguarding team.
</p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-394_ pf-heading-1-h3">Training courses for trustees
</h3><p class="sc-iLLNPL dGtRC pf-396_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Trustees can benefit from tailored courses covering governance, compliance, and leadership skills. These courses help them fulfil their roles effectively and ensure the integrity of their organisations.
